@startuml
[*] --> Unbound
Unbound --> BotInstallStarted : teacher clicks add bot
BotInstallStarted --> InstallCancelled : Discord OAuth cancelled
BotInstallStarted --> RawGuildSaved : callback returns guild_id
RawGuildSaved --> GuildSynced : sync worker fetches metadata/channels
GuildSynced --> GuildSelected : teacher selects owned guild
GuildSelected --> ChannelValidating : notification/voice channels selected
ChannelValidating --> InvalidSelection : channel not in guild or wrong type
InvalidSelection --> GuildSelected : choose again
ChannelValidating --> Bound : save class_discord_binding
Bound --> Bound : update channels
Bound --> Unbound : teacher unbinds
Bound --> SyncStale : sync worker cannot access guild
SyncStale --> GuildSynced : access restored
SyncStale --> Unbound : teacher unbinds
InstallCancelled --> Unbound
@enduml
